<paragraph blockId="6.[264,1323,1364,1870]" pageId="6" pageNumber="7">
<emphasis bold="true" box="[320,434,1524,1550]" pageId="6" pageNumber="7">Remarks</emphasis>
. A single 
<typeStatus box="[561,652,1524,1550]" pageId="6" pageNumber="7">syntype</typeStatus>
is deposited in NMHN but was not available for study. The conspecifity of 
<taxonomicName authorityName="Abeille de Perrin" authorityYear="1897" box="[507,647,1564,1589]" class="Insecta" family="Buprestidae" genus="Agrilus" kingdom="Animalia" order="Coleoptera" pageId="6" pageNumber="7" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="croaticus">
<emphasis box="[507,647,1564,1589]" italics="true" pageId="6" pageNumber="7">A. croaticus</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
and 
<taxonomicName authorityName="Obenberger" authorityYear="1927" box="[709,839,1564,1589]" class="Insecta" family="Buprestidae" genus="Agrilus" kingdom="Animalia" order="Coleoptera" pageId="6" pageNumber="7" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="serbicus">
<emphasis box="[709,839,1564,1589]" italics="true" pageId="6" pageNumber="7">A. serbicus</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
is based on the generally accepted concept of 
<emphasis box="[352,500,1604,1629]" italics="true" pageId="6" pageNumber="7">
<taxonomicName authorityName="Abeille de Perrin" authorityYear="1897" box="[352,497,1604,1629]" class="Insecta" family="Buprestidae" genus="Agrilus" kingdom="Animalia" order="Coleoptera" pageId="6" pageNumber="7" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="croaticus">A. croaticus</taxonomicName>
.
</emphasis>
</paragraph>
</subSubSection>
