<subSubSection pageId="7" pageNumber="8" type="discussion">
<paragraph blockId="7.[264,1323,283,710]" pageId="7" pageNumber="8">
<emphasis bold="true" box="[320,434,363,389]" pageId="7" pageNumber="8">Remarks</emphasis>
. 
<taxonomicName authorityName="Obenberger" authorityYear="1913" box="[450,609,364,389]" class="Insecta" family="Buprestidae" genus="Agrilus" kingdom="Animalia" order="Coleoptera" pageId="7" pageNumber="8" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="curtii">
<emphasis box="[450,609,364,389]" italics="true" pageId="7" pageNumber="8">Agrilus curtii</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
was described from multiple localities “Uj­Pest; Bisamberg bei 
<collectingRegion box="[309,375,404,430]" country="Austria" name="Wien" pageId="7" pageNumber="8">Wien</collectingRegion>
; 
<collectingRegion box="[389,451,404,430]" country="Austria" name="Wien" pageId="7" pageNumber="8">Wien</collectingRegion>
Umgebung”. The type locality becomes the place of origin of the 
<typeStatus pageId="7" pageNumber="8">lectotype</typeStatus>
. The name 
<taxonomicName authorityName="Obenberger" authorityYear="1913" box="[454,517,444,469]" class="Insecta" family="Buprestidae" genus="Agrilus" kingdom="Animalia" order="Coleoptera" pageId="7" pageNumber="8" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="curtii">
<emphasis box="[454,517,444,469]" italics="true" pageId="7" pageNumber="8">curtii</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
was cited by 
<bibRefCitation author="Bily, S." box="[681,817,444,470]" pageId="7" pageNumber="8" pagination="5 - 172" refId="ref14966" refString="Bily, S. (1993) Byrrhidae, Buprestidae, p. 71, 73 - 75. In: Jelinek, J., Check-list of Czechoslovak Insects IV (Coleoptera). Folia Heyrovskyana, Supplementum 1, 5 - 172." type="journal article" year="1993">Bílý (1993)</bibRefCitation>
as a synonym of 
<emphasis box="[1025,1173,444,469]" italics="true" pageId="7" pageNumber="8">
<taxonomicName authorityName="Abeille de Perrin" authorityYear="1897" box="[1025,1170,444,469]" class="Insecta" family="Buprestidae" genus="Agrilus" kingdom="Animalia" order="Coleoptera" pageId="7" pageNumber="8" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="croaticus">A. croaticus</taxonomicName>
.
</emphasis>
<bibRefCitation author="Muhle, H. &amp; Brandl, P. &amp; Niehuis, M." pageId="7" pageNumber="8" refId="ref17447" refString="Muhle, H., Brandl, P. &amp; Niehuis, M. (2000) Catalogus faunae Graeciae. Coleoptera, Buprestidae. Augsburg, Roble, 254 pp." type="book" year="2000">Mühle et al. (2000)</bibRefCitation>
studied types of both taxa and reconfirmed their conspecifity. 
<bibRefCitation author="Bily, S." box="[1096,1233,484,510]" pageId="7" pageNumber="8" pagination="1 - 104" refId="ref15011" refString="Bily, S. (2002) Summary of the bionomy of the Buprestid beetles of Central Europe (Coleoptera: Buprestidae). Acta Entomologica Musaei Nationalis Pragae, Supplement 10, 1 - 104, 16 col. pls." type="journal article" year="2002">Bílý (2002)</bibRefCitation>
treated 
<taxonomicName authorityName="Obenberger" authorityYear="1913" box="[264,359,524,549]" class="Insecta" family="Buprestidae" genus="Agrilus" kingdom="Animalia" order="Coleoptera" pageId="7" pageNumber="8" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="curtii">
<emphasis box="[264,359,524,549]" italics="true" pageId="7" pageNumber="8">A. curtii</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
as a valid species without further explanation.
</paragraph>
</subSubSection>
